sources.title: THE RAGTIME BAND (1913)
sources.description: THE RAGTIME BAND Keystone-Mutual 1 reel, rel. May 1, 1913 (the Band) also the Jazz Band dir. Mack Sennett cast: Mabel Normand, Ford Sterling, Alice Davenport, Nick Cogley finished 3/27/1913 Note. The version for .avi download here is somewhat better in picture quality than the one presented on video.
